<h1>WHO WE ARE</h1>
<p>Temple Beth Tikvah takes pride in being the center of 
Jewish life in North Orange County. TBT's mission is to 
encourage and promote the continuity of our rich Jewish 
heritage and traditions. Our congregation, working along 
with the larger Jewish community, creates the environment 
and the opportunities to gather together for prayer, for 
meaningful lifelong Jewish learning, and for social 
interactions and cultural experiences.</p>